rmediateField</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inclusion</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_le_K₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">lemma</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">normal_intersect</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Normal</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Normal</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Normal</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁interK₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rename_i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">fk</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ins1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ins2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">normal_iff</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IsAlgebraic</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">isIntegral</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">replace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">normal_iff</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_toK₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">replace</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h2'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">normal_iff</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_toK₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">minpoly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_toK₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">minpoly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">minpoly</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">algHom_eq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_toK₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IntermediateField</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inclusion_injective</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_le_K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1'</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">minpoly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_toK₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">minpoly</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">minpoly</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">algHom_eq</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_toK₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IntermediateField</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">inclusion_injective</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">K₁intK₂_le_K₂</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₂</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">at</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h2'</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IntermediateField</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">splits_of_splits</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">exact</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Polynomial</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">splits_of_algHom</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">F</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">L</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">K</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h1'</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">K₁</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">val</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">intro</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rootK</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hrootK</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">apply</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">IntermediateField</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mem_inf</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"k\">have</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Polynomial</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mem_rootSet</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hrootK</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n<span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"bp\">·</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Excercise</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The first <code>sorry</code> demands to show that <code>K₁interK₂</code> is algebraic over F (this is because K₁ is algebraic). The second and third is about proving roots of <code>minpoly F x</code> are in K₁ and K₂ (this is because <code>minpoly F x</code> splits over both K₁ and K₂). Thanks in advance for your kind help! <br>\nAnd, btw, I somehow find the field and polynomial part in mathlib is particularly hard to understand and utilize, are there any suggestions on how to improve my capabilities in doing field problems in Lean?</p>",
