        "content": "<p>You might find it easier to go via the normal closure. Apply <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=IntermediateField.normalClosure_of_normal#doc\">docs#IntermediateField.normalClosure_of_normal</a> to <code>K₁</code> and <code>K₂</code>, and apply <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=IntermediateField.le_normalClosure#doc\">docs#IntermediateField.le_normalClosure</a> and <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=IntermediateField.normalClosure_mono#doc\">docs#IntermediateField.normalClosure_mono</a> to the intersection.</p>",
